{"article_id":"LPHhXa5JgQ111mrv","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"8:54 p.m. |","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Updated","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"John E. Bryson announced his resignation as President Obama ' s commerce secretary on Thursday ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"citing medical reasons after an episode","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"in which he had a seizure","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"and was involved in a sequence of car crashes .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Bryson , a longtime California electricity conglomerate executive , served in the cabinet for just eight months","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"and had kept a low profile in Washington during his short tenure .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"But that changed","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"when he was found unconscious behind the wheel of his car in California earlier this month","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"after reportedly hitting two other vehicles .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Although tests for Mr. Bryson are continuing ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"a Commerce Department official said","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"a neurologist has diagnosed a complex partial seizure ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"which can affect brain function","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"and leave a person in a state of confusion .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"He had never had a seizure before","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"and did not have any known health ailments ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"the official said ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"and he had limited recollection of the episode .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"After initially taking a medical leave ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Mr. Bryson decided on Wednesday to step down from his job","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"and talked with Mr. Obama by telephone that night .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"He then sent the president a letter","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"making his decision formal ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"and announced it on Thursday morning to department employees .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"\" The work","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that you do","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"to help America ' s entrepreneurs and businesses build our economy and create jobs","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"is more important now than ever","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"and I have come to the conclusion","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that I need to step down","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"to prevent distractions from this critical mission , \"","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Bryson wrote to his staff .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Mr. Obama released a statement","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"in which he thanked Mr. Bryson","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and invited him to the Oval Office","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to pose for pictures ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"but neither man made any comments or took questions .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"\" As secretary , John fought tirelessly for our nation ' s businesses and workers ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"helping to bolster our exports","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and promote American manufacturing and products at home and abroad , \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Obama said in the written statement .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Rebecca M. Blank , the deputy commerce secretary","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"who has been serving as acting secretary","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"since Mr. Bryson took a leave ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"will continue to run the department , with its $ 7.5 billion budget and 47,000 employees worldwide .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Given the short time","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"left","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"before Congress leaves town for the fall election campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"it may be difficult for the president to recruit , vet , nominate and confirm a permanent replacement .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"The White House heaped praise on Ms. Blank ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"and Mr. Obama could leave her in place until after the election ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"when he will know","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"whether he has a second term .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Given the political attention on the economy , however ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"he may feel pressed to name a nominee before then .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Mr. Bryson , 68 , the former chief executive of Edison International in Southern California and a founder of the Natural Resources Defense Council , was nominated in May 2011","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and , after a brief struggle in the Senate , was confirmed last October .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"While in office , he summarized his priority with the phrase","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"\" build it here","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and sell it everywhere , \"","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"focusing on supporting manufacturing , increasing exports","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"and encouraging more companies to locate or expand operations in the United States .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"He eschewed the Washington scene ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"spending much of his time","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"visiting businesses across the country .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Democrats praised him on Thursday","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"and Republicans , in deference to his health , generally remained quiet .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"\" I have great respect for John and his desire","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"to resign in an effort","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"to make sure","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"there are no distractions toward job growth","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"and advancing America ' s businesses and entrepreneurs for a full economic recovery , \"","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"Senator John D. Rockefeller IV , a West Virginia Democrat and chairman of the commerce committee , said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"Mr. Bryson ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"who has a home in San Marino , Calif. ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"was there","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"to deliver a commencement address at the private school","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"his four daughters had attended","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"when he experienced the seizure .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Driving a Lexus in suburban San Gabriel on June 9 ,","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"Mr. Bryson rolled into the back of a Buick","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"waiting at a train crossing ,","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"according to authorities .","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"After talking briefly with the other driver ,","depth":16},{"id":87,"text":"he got back into his car","depth":16},{"id":88,"text":"and hit the Buick again","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"as he was driving off ,","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"the police said .","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"Minutes later , he crashed into the rear of another car about two miles away .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"Mr. Bryson was cited for a hit-and-run accident .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Authorities reported no indications of illegal drugs or alcohol ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"although they were waiting for final tests .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"No one was seriously hurt ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"and damage to the cars was minor .","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":193,"left":98,"right":192,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":2,"right":191,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":191,"left":115,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":101,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":3,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":4,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":114,"left":105,"right":113,"relati